FNB has announced that eBucks Rewards members can now book domestic and international flights directly through the FNB app. “The travel offering emphasises our commitment to addressing the needs of customers through a trusted, safer and convenient platform,” said FNB Retail CEO Raj Makanjee. “The proposition significantly expands the value we give customers and their families, in line with our focus on family banking.” eBucks Rewards members can expect discounts of up to 40% on flights, and can also manage their bookings, view their discounts, and maintain family profiles from within the app. “Booking, paying and managing flights for yourself, your family or even your friends has really become easy to do on the FNB App,” said eBucks Rewards CEO Johan Moolman. “We look forward to expanding on this and providing even more value to our customers.”